CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Concentration of Poverty School Grant Program – Personnel and Per Pupil
3 Grants – Eligible Uses
4 FOR the purpose of repealing the limitation on the authorization to use personnel grants
5 and per pupil grants under the Concentration of Poverty School Grant Program to
6 provide certain fine arts instructional programs through a certain fiscal year; and
7 generally relating to the Concentration of Poverty School Grant Program.
8 BY repealing and reenacting, without amendments,
